"Marka aad is-haysato Grylli, waxaad mas'uul ka tahay inaad hubiso in xogta "
"isticmaale oo dhami la kayadiyo lana farsameeyo si waafaqsan dhib-dhaqanka "
"asturta ku saabsan."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:54
msgid ""
"This notice was last updated in June 2025 and may evolve to reflect changes "
"in the software or regulatory landscape."
msgstr ""
"Ogeysiiskani wuxuu ahaa kii ugu dambeeyay ee la cusbooneysiiyo Juun 2025 "
