#: app/templates/admin/index.html:43
msgid "⚠️ Admin Tips"
msgstr "⚠️ Talooyinka Maamulka"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:45
msgid ""
"Never run in production with DEBUG enabled. Debug mode exposes internal "
"details and stack traces."
msgstr ""
"Waligaa ha ku socodsiin wax soo saar iyadoo DEBUG ay tahay mid karti leh. "
"Habka Debug wuxuu muujinayaa faahfaahinta gudaha iyo raadad xadka."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:47
msgid ""
"Always deploy Grylli behind a reverse proxy (e.g. Caddy, Nginx, or Traefik) "
"and serve it over HTTPS. Sensitive user data must be encrypted in transit."
msgstr ""
"Had iyo jeer ku kororsada Grylli gunta madaxa kale (e.g. Caddy, Nginx, ama "
"Traefik) oo ku adeeg HTTPS. Xogta adag ee isticmaalaha waa in si qarsoodiya "
"loo gudbiyaa."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:50
msgid ""
"Ensure the data folder (database) is backed up regularly. Backups are stored"
" in the 'backups' folder."
msgstr "Hubi folderka xogta (keydka macluumaadka) uu gurmad yahay hoostagaaga"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:53
msgid ""
"The uploads folder is shared. To isolate attachments per user, configure "
"host-level directories and access controls."
msgstr ""
"Galahayaga uploads-ka waxaa wadaago. Si looga soocayo lifaaxayaashee "
"isticmaalaha, qaabey dheerayaal heer xoste iyo xakamaynta galitaanada."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:55
msgid ""
"To restore a backup: stop the container, replace the grylli.db file from a "
"backup, and restart."
msgstr ""
"Si aad u soo celiso kaydka: jooji weelka, beddel xogta/grylli.db mid ka mid "
"ah galka kaydadka, oo dib u bilaab weelka."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:56
msgid ""
"Admins cannot remove their own admin role to prevent accidental lockout."
msgstr ""
"Maamulayaasha ma awoodaan inay iska qaadaan doorka maamulaha si looga "
"hortago in si khaldan loo xiryo."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:58
msgid ""
"Rate limits and automatic account lockouts are enforced to protect against "
"brute-force login attempts."
msgstr ""
"Xaddidooyinka heerka iyo xayiraadaha koontadu waxaa lagu dabaqay si looga "
"ilaaliyo isku-dayada galitaan qasabka ah."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:60
msgid ""
"Passwords, SMTP credentials, and API tokens are encrypted at rest using "
"Fernet."
msgstr ""
"Passwords, ogaysiisyada SMTP, iyo tokens API ayaa lagu siray marka la nasiyo"
" iyadoo la isticmaalayo Fernet."

